Global Fruit Intelligent Sorting Equipment Market Insights
Fruit Intelligent Sorting Equipment Market size was valued at USD 1.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.5 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 10.2% from 2024 to 2030.

Fruit Intelligent Sorting Equipment Market Overview
The global Fruit Intelligent Sorting Equipment market is valued at USD 1.2 billion in 2023 and is expected to grow at a CAGR of 8.2% from 2023 to 2030, reaching an estimated market size of USD 2.5 billion by 2030. This market growth is driven by the increasing demand for automation and efficiency in the agricultural industry, especially in fruit processing and sorting operations. These systems help reduce labor costs, improve sorting accuracy, and enhance production efficiency. As global food demand rises, the adoption of intelligent sorting technologies in the fruit industry is expected to significantly increase.

